trans-unit.source: Specifies the source for <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox" /> automatic completion functionality.
trans-unit.target: Especifica a origem para a funcionalidade de preenchimento automático de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> e <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox" />.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the equivalent of <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.FileSystem" /> and <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.AllUrl" /> as the source.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o equivalente de <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.FileSystem" /> e <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.AllUrl" /> como a origem.

trans-unit.source: This is the default value when <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteMode" /> has been set to a value other than the default.
trans-unit.target: Esse é o valor padrão quando <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteMode" /> for definido como um valor diferente do padrão.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the equivalent of <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.HistoryList" /> and <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.RecentlyUsedList" /> as the source.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o equivalente de <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.HistoryList" /> e <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.RecentlyUsedList" /> como a origem.

trans-unit.source: Specifies strings from a built-in <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteStringCollection" /> as the source.
trans-unit.target: Especifica as cadeias de caracteres de um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteStringCollection" /> interno como a origem.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the file system as the source.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o sistema de arquivos como a origem.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that only directory names and not file names will be automatically completed.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que somente os nomes de diretório e não nomes de arquivo serão automaticamente preenchidos.

trans-unit.source: Includes the Uniform Resource Locators (URLs) in the history list.
trans-unit.target: Inclui os URLs (Uniform Resource Locators) na lista de histórico.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the items of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> represent the source.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que os itens do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> representam a origem.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that no <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource" /> is currently in use.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que nenhum <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource" /> está atualmente em uso.

trans-unit.source: This is the default value of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource" />.
trans-unit.target: Esse é o valor padrão de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource" />.

trans-unit.source: Includes the Uniform Resource Locators (URLs) in the list of those URLs most recently used.
trans-unit.target: Inclui os URLs (Uniform Resource Locators) na lista de URLs usados mais recentemente.
